{"tid":680578,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"科大推廣文, 你問人地答","createTime":"2018-05-27T09:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T13:29:18.000Z","uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb345dca67cd28b48190cd9e320b92bfc013279","tid":680578,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"科大已經步入final 既尾聲 又係時候推廣下科大俾大家<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE既同學仔大家好, 唔知你地諗好入咩大學同讀咩科未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日我開呢個post就係為大家打打氣, 順便同大家介紹下科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 科大名聲好, 排名高<br />\n科大, 別名<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Asia MIT, 香港第0</span></span><br />\n根據QS排名, 科大<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">曾經</span></span>超越港大成為左香港第0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科大既engine同business係17年既排名更加比港大個排名高唔少<br />\n第時入到科大比d豬朋狗友問你出路, 你都絕對可以好驕傲咁講我讀科大啊, 相信唔少人都會讀你叻仔叻女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 科大學術氣氛好<br />\n大家咁辛苦入到大學梗係想追求更多既知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科大係呢方面就訓練到學生十分著重讀書, 每星期都安排唔同既功課同測驗比學生溫故而知新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以見到既就係同學落堂去就擁埋去教授到問書, 問完就會去拉把溫習, 同學之間都會有各種既學術討論, 係咁既氛圍底下, 你GPA都自然會高啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 科大男女比例均衡<br />\n街外人經常流傳科大係咩少林寺啊, 格劍聖地等<br />\n呢d其實都係唔太正確既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以business school為例, 16intake<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男女比例為47:53, 53既仲要係女黎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試想像下上堂acct堂, 前後左右都係女既話, 你每堂都有動力去上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fundergrad.bm.ust.hk%2Feng%2Fwhy%2Fstudents%2Four_students%2Findex.jsp&d=GXNzoZh0xSHPFw8hkR3%2Bf4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=3d387320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n再聽下幾個名人分享科大:<br />\n1. 嶺大分數, 三大名氣/engine就是ust(鍵盤騎士, 2015) <br />\n相信大家都聽過呢類型既說話, 想用大學黎證明自己能力, 科大絕對係你既首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 港大張xx/鏗x都同鍵騎有唔少交情, 佢地都好支持鍵騎入讀科大civil, 認為係明智之選<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE同學仔聽完係咪心動呢, 如果係就請立即登入JUPAS Account, 更改你既選擇至JS5xxxx (任何你心儀既科大科目)<br />\n祝福你地DSE都能順利渡過, 9月係科大呢個大家庭見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit to: 銀河的夏天雨姐姐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/178391/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/178391/page/1</a><br />\n有咩問題 你都可以搵銀河姐姐問架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9496579fc830266c4674f774a9a9b31e6dd473c","tid":680578,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fce0564fc59a10435ca26a65358f359aba48d55","tid":680578,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9496579fc830266c4674f774a9a9b31e6dd473c","tid":680578,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:40:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"Shitty U 完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcde8a139c45287d90aa551b6649d6ccd89b60b0","tid":680578,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"最後忠告: 大家千其千其一定要入科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}